title: SKYRIM AT WAR - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #1
description:
SKYRIM AT WAR - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #1 - Welcome Nords to the start of a brand new Elder Scrolls Campiagn! We will be leading the Stormcloaks against the Tamriel Empire.  It is time for this bloody Civil War to come to a close! It's time for the Nords to take back Skyrim!  Enjoy the Video :D

Mod link: http://www.moddb.com/mods/the-elder-scrolls-total-war

Unofficial Patch: http://www.twcenter.net/forums/showthread.php?750685-Sub-mod-Unofficial-TES-Patch-1-3-DOWNLOAD-LINK

JOIN MY DISCORD SERVER: https://discord.gg/JjR7UR3
